{"tid":1935703,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"送給義士手足的一首改歌","createTime":"2020-03-20T18:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T20:55:00.000Z","uid":46420,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90a0b4dfeb00295bfe6e9729816ec64f76f16ce4","tid":1935703,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"原曲:勇  楊千嬅<br />\n<br />\n你我都已大無畏　<br />\n奮勇抗爭不怕死<br />\n就算在浪漫熱血之時　<br />\n情況險要&nbsp; 仍然佔領　<br />\n為理念搏盡條命<br />\n<br />\n砌你不用合情理　<br />\n毅進用獸性本能咬撚住你<br />\n只想到姦淫咗你　<br />\n還手執血腥利器<br />\n突然亂入拗斷你雙臂<br />\n<br />\n旁人初不贊同　<br />\n說法理也不容<br />\n為理念投入　<br />\n傷都不怕痛<br />\n人人發一個夢　<br />\n泛民聯同激進<br />\n亦不及義士你那麼勇<br />\n<br />\n難忘頭盔染紅　<br />\n仍無阻擋去路<br />\n望著部鐵馬　<br />\n痴根亂柒衝<br />\n你抹去溫柔　<br />\n唯獨留下點英勇<br />\n<br />\n義士不望被憐愛　<br />\n亦自願化作英雄去保護你<br />\n勳章我早留給你　<br />\n為你願意撐下去<br />\n傲然笑著為你擋兵器<br />\n<br />\n你下來我上去　<br />\n在路上穿梭中<br />\n散仔只可撲空　<br />\n踢佢屎忽個窿<br />\n<br />\n我定會支援　<br />\n還謝你這麼英勇<br />\n發夢過的人　<br />\n全部變得很英勇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw主要其實係想改首歌讚揚下各位義士,為手足打打氣,所以比較少搞笑成份,大家如果覺得有邊句太過教會,歡迎各位指正提醒,謝謝!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n勿忘義士 621 721 811 831 929 101 1111 1118<br />\n</span></span><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"20e490878a0f0b6fb27d51cdcf6390354a38dd83","tid":1935703,"uid":204272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"推 支持你"},{"pid":"1ea7397bfd1f936dc0124d47ea2f959c429e1ac0","tid":1935703,"uid":129273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"本人胸無點墨唔識改歌,但幫你推PO,睇下有無人唱咗佢放youtube!!<br />\n<br />\n推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a13dac38d25fbce04ce1bc787f4c5bc3313ebd","tid":1935703,"uid":46420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20e490878a0f0b6fb27d51cdcf6390354a38dd83","tid":1935703,"uid":204272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"推 支持你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"謝謝,有唔啱音或意見歡迎指正!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4709252ce1caba76730eb4a92fb2d312d8e84338","tid":1935703,"uid":46420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ea7397bfd1f936dc0124d47ea2f959c429e1ac0","tid":1935703,"uid":129273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"本人胸無點墨唔識改歌,但幫你推PO,睇下有無人唱咗佢放youtube!!<br />\n<br />\n推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"手足有心啦,謝謝!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c713c422dbf9571a1b063cb232fc1b98d1a245","tid":1935703,"uid":204272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a13dac38d25fbce04ce1bc787f4c5bc3313ebd","tid":1935703,"uid":46420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20e490878a0f0b6fb27d51cdcf6390354a38dd83","tid":1935703,"uid":204272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"推 支持你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"謝謝,有唔啱音或意見歡